metadata.name: Weasel Happiness
metadata.description:
Happiness is hanging on the rope. the smell of the laundry is mixed with the poppy flowers, spreading happiness on the rope. A family on a swing takes happiness to the sky. Sometimes we should seek happiness not in what we seek, but in what is in our lives. one rope is seventy to this happiness..

Photographer: Beytullah ELES
